content:
I think I'll check out The Egg & I. I've heard of them before and their menu sounds pretty appealing. Plus, it's great that they have outdoor seating. I'll make sure to get there early to grab a table. Thanks for the rec!

By the way, do you know if they take reservations or is it first come, first served? And are they pretty quick with their service, or should we plan to spend a few hours there?
